  <h1>Tones</h1>
  <p>Vowels in Khoekhoe also have different tones.  There are three types of tones, high tones /v́/, mid tones /v/ and low tones /v̀/ (note that 'v' stands for vowel, and mid tones are unmarked).  There are six combinations of tones based on the morae (m = mora): ḿḿ, ḿm, mḿ, mm, m̀ḿ, and m̀m</p>
